title: Shah Rukh Khan launches official logo of ‘Fan’
text: Shah Rukh Khan launches official logo of ‘Fan’ Friday, 23 October 2015 (3 minutes ago) Shah Rukh Khan has launched the official logo of Yash Raj Films' "Fan," which features the photographs of his real life admirers. Shah Rukh Khan's upcoming film 'Fan' teaser will be releasing on SRK's birthday this year 2015.
